HEADWORD: Bewitchment
<hw>Be*witch"ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of bewitching, or the state of being bewitched.</def>
<rj><au>Tylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The power of bewitching or charming.</def>
